prediction.sparql:
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?art_form ?label WHERE {
  fb:m.04lg6 fb:visual_art.visual_artist.art_forms ?art_form .
  ?art_form rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( lang( ?label ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?profession ?profession_label WHERE {
  fb:m.09482 fb:people.person.profession ?profession .
  ?profession rdfs:label ?profession_label .
  FILTER ( lang( ?profession_label ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?team ?teamLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.095xk6 fb:people.person.education ?edu .
  ?edu fb:education.education.institution fb:m.01vs5c .
  fb:m.01vs5c fb:education.educational_institution.sports_teams ?team .
  ?team fb:type.object.type fb:american_football.football_team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?teamLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?season ?season_label ?from WHERE {
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.character fb:m.093xn8 .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.series fb:m.03m8sg .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.seasons ?season .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.from ?from .
  ?season rdfs:label ?season_label
  FILTER ( lang( ?season_label ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( ?season_label , "Season 3" ) )
}
ORDER BY ?from
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?anthem ?label WHERE {
  fb:m.0d060g fb:location.country.national_anthem ?anthem .
  ?anthem rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( lang( ?label ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( REGEX( ?label , '^\\w+ \\w+$' ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?year WHERE {
  ?campaign fb:government.election_campaign.election fb:m.07vx3 .
  fb:m.09b6zr fb:government.politician.election_campaigns ?campaign .
  fb:m.07vx3 fb:government.election.election_year ?date .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date ) AS ?year )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?superbowl ?date WHERE {
  fb:m.01ct6 fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?superbowl .
  ?superbowl fb:type.object.type fb:m.01xljv1 .
  ?superbowl fb:time.event.start_date ?date .
}
ORDER BY ?date

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?institution WHERE {
  fb:m.0c2yrf fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution ?institution .
  ?institution fb:type.object.type fb:education.educational_institution .
  ?institution fb:common.topic.notable_types fb:m.01y2hnl .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?performance ?actor ?language WHERE {
  ?performance fb:film.dubbing_performance.film fb:m.0fdv3 .
  ?performance fb:film.dubbing_performance.character fb:m.0f2y0 .
  ?performance fb:film.dubbing_performance.actor ?actor .
  ?performance fb:film.dubbing_performance.language ?language .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?region ?regionLabel WHERE {
  ?region fb:location.location.contains fb:m.05kkh .
  ?region rdfs:label ?regionLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?regionLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?team WHERE {
  fb:m.0d81yf fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.from ?from .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.to ?to .
  FILTER ( ( ?from <= "2010-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?to >= "2010-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) || ( ?from <= "2010-12-31" ^^ xsd:gYear && ?to >= "2010-01-01" ^^ xsd:gYear ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?championship ?date WHERE {
  fb:m.0jmfb fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?date
}
ORDER BY ?date
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?notableObject ?notableObjectLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.083pr fb:common.topic.notable_for ?notableFor .
  ?notableFor fb:common.notable_for.notable_object ?notableObject .
  ?notableObject rdfs:label ?notableObjectLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?notableObjectLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?marriage ?spouse WHERE {
  fb:m.03p77 fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.from ?from .
}
ORDER BY ASC ( ?from )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?event ?startDate WHERE {
  fb:m.0713r fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?event .
  ?event rdfs:label ?eventLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?eventLabel ) , "world series" ) ) ?event fb:time.event.start_date ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1
